This is how I did it:

1. Go to the adobe installation, intall it, run adobe photoshop cs2.

2. Photshop at the moment thinks its a trial, to make it the full version, get the activation box up in the help tab.

3. Tell it to activate, if the online doesn't work, it will transfer to phone method.

4. In the folder that was downloaded go to the CRACK folder, then to the keygen.

5. Type in the serial number (in the activation by phone box on photoshop) into the keygen.

6. Do the same with the activation code

7. Generate the auth code on the keygen, then type that in on the photoshop activation box, on the auth bar.

DONE!

The steps I took to make it work for me.
1. Download Torrents.
2. Double click 'Setup' and install program.
3. Open the program.
4. When it Asks For Serial Enter This:
    1045-1081-1585-9237-5709-1315 
5. *a window will pop asks you to activate !
    *click activation options
    *then check via phone.....then click next.
There will be 2 sets of numbers on this page.
6. Go to 'Crack' File & open 'KeyGen'
7. Type the 2 numbers supplied in the CS2 
    activation window. Then click 'Generate
    Auth   Code'
8. Enter the Authorization Code that was
    generated into the CS2 Activation window.
